cs.GR, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL

The paper deals with 3D modeling and uses neural networks for suggesting complementary components and their placement for an incomplete 3D part assembly. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) and Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of neural network architectures, which suggests that it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with natural language processing and user preferences, which suggests that it could also belong to the Computation and Language (cs.CL) sub-category.
